						<summary>

						<p>This is much damaged. It seems to record an endowment made by <hi rend="bold">[Ku]kāri Sundari</hi> wife of a native <hi rend="bold">of Pugaḻiyūr</hi> for feeding Brāhmaṇas on the days of <hi rend="italic">dvādas11i</hi> through the agency of <hi rend="italic">Dvādas11i-Gaṇapperumakkaḷ</hi> at Tiruchcheṅgōḍu.</p>						

